    <briefdescription>
<para>Object to hold components needed in all fft based decon algorithms. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The fft based algorithms implemented here us the GNU Scientific Library prime factorization fft algorithm. Those methods require initialization given length of the fft to load and store the factorization data. This object holds these for all such methods and recomputes them only when needed for efficiency. <linebreak/>
 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
